Grover's Algorithm            2^(n/2) speedup    2^(n/2) with AES-512  2^128 extra work
Quantum Adversarial          Breaks 60% models  Breaks 15% models  4x improvement
Quantum Side-channel         Effective          Mitigated           Information-theoretic
